 "html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n<title>Invoice</title>\n<style>\n    body {\n        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\n        margin: 0;\n        padding: 0;\n    }\n\n    .container {\n        max-width: 800px;\n        margin: 0 auto;\n        padding: 20px;\n    }\n\n    .header {\n        text-align: left;\n        margin-bottom: 20px;\n    }\n\n    .logo-container {\n        display: flex;\n        justify-content: space-between;\n    }\n\n    .logo {\n        max-width: 200px;\n    }\n\n    .address {\n        font-size: 12px;\n    }\n\n    .letter {\n        text-align: center;\n        margin-top: 20px;\n    }\n    \n        .line {\n        margin-bottom: 2px;\n  text-align: left\n    }\n   .line2 {\n  margin-bottom:2px;\n  text-align: left\n    }\n\n    .labels {\n        display: inline-block;\n        width: 220px;\n  font-size: 12px\n    }\n\n    .colon {\n        margin-right: 10px;\n    }\n  .colon2 {\n        margin-right: 15px;\n    }\n  .colon3 {\n        margin-left: 80px;\n    }\n  .colon4 {\n        margin-left: 10px;\n    }\n  .section p {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding-left: 20px;\n            text-indent: -20px; /* Negative text-indent to pull back the second line */\n        }\n        .footer {\n        background-color: #ff8a3a;\n        \n        padding: 5px;\n        text-align: center;\n        border: 1px solid #e8823d;\n    }\n\n    .footer-text {\n        font-weight: bold;\n  \t\tfont-size: 10px;\n        color: white;\n        display: inline-block;\n    }\n    \n    /*style page 2*/\n            .section2.line {\n        margin-bottom: 2px;\n  text-align: left\n    }\n   .section2.line2 {\n  margin-bottom:2px;\n  text-align: left\n    }\n  .section2.line3 {\n  margin-bottom:20px;\n  text-align: left\n    }\n\n    .section2.labels {\n        display: inline-block;\n        width: 70px;\n        font-weight: bold;\n    }\n.section2.labels1 {\n        display: inline-block;\n        width: 40%;\n        \n    }\n    .section2.colon {\n        margin-right: 10px;\n    }\n  .section2.colon2 {\n        margin-right: 15px;\n    }\n  .section2.colon3 {\n        margin-right: 70px;\n  }\n</style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"header\">\n            <p>Authorised Sales & Service Parts Dealer</p>\n            <div class=\"logo-container\">\n                <div>\n                    <img class=\"logo\" src=\"https://dcautoservices.mydotconsulting.com/files/perodua-logo.png\" alt=\"Company Logo 1\" width=\"200\">\n                    \n                </div>\n                <!--\n                <img class=\"logo\" src=\"\" alt=\"Company Logo 2\" width=\"200\" height=\"45\">\n                -->\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"letter\">\n                \n                 <p style=\"text-align: center;\">   <strong>INDIVIDUAL LETTER OF INDEMNITY</strong></p><br>\n                   <div class=\"line\">\n                    <span class=\"labels\">Date</span><span class=\"colon\">:</span>\n                    <span>{{ frappe.utils.formatdate(doc.date, \"dd MMMM yyyy\") }}</span>\n                </div>\n                   <br>\n                   <div class=\"line\">\n                    <span class=\"font-size:12px\">AMBANK (M) BERHAD / AMBANK ISLAMIC BERHAD</span>\n                </div>\n                     <br>\n                <div class=\"line\">\n                    <span class=\"labels\">LOAN ACCOUNT NO</span><span class=\"colon2\">:</span>\n                    <span><b>{{doc.loan_account_number}}</b></span>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"line\">\n                    <span class=\"labels\">ENGINE NO</span><span class=\"colon2\">:</span>\n                    <span><b>\n                        {% if doc.engine_no %}\n                            {{ doc.engine_no }}\n                        {% else %}\n                            &nbsp;\n                        {% endif %}\n                    </b></span>\n                </div>\n                   <div class=\"line2\">\n                    <span class=\"labels\">CHASSIS NO</span><span class=\"colon2\">:</span>\n                    <span >\n                      <b>{% if doc.chassis %}\n                            {{ doc.chassis }}\n                        {% else %}\n                            &nbsp;\n                        {% endif %}\n                      </b></span>\n                </div>\n      <div class=\"line2\">\n                    <span class=\"labels\">MAKE & MODEL OF VEHICLE</span><span class=\"colon2\">:</span>\n        <span ><b>{{doc.model}}</b></span>\n                </div>\n               <div class=\"line2\">\n                    <span class=\"labels\">NAME OF HIRER</span><span class=\"colon2\">:</span>\n                    <span><b>{{doc.customer_name}}</b></span>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"line2\">\n                    <span class=\"labels\">NRIC/CO./BUS. REG NO</span><span class=\"colon2\">:</span>\n                  <span ><b>{{doc.nric_company_business_reg_no}}</b></span>\n                </div>\n              \n      <br>\n     \n                    \n      <p style=\"text-align: left;padding-bottom:15px;font-size:12px\">We hereby confirm that the Hirer has settled in full the differential sum between the selling price of the vehicle and the hire purchase loan amount, and in consideration of your agreeing at out request to up-lift the e Ownership of above chassis number from Financial Information Services to enables us to register the vehicle to the above-named hirer with your ownership prior to the full settlement of the loan account, and we undertake the following:</p>\n                     \n        <p style=\"text-align: left;padding-bottom:10px;font-size:12px\">1. To keep you indemnified against any losses that may be incurred by you in up-lifting the e-Ownership and in releasing the registration documents to us.</p> \n        <p style=\"text-align: left;padding-bottom:10px;font-size:12px\">2. To deliver to you the Vehicle Ownership Certificate duly registered to the hirer's name with your ownership endorsed therein together with the duly signed hire-purchase agreement and all relevant documents within forteen (14) days from the date of upliftment of the e-Ownership by you.</p>\n        <p style=\"text-align: left;padding-bottom:10px;font-size:12px\">3. To authorize you to set-off the proceeds from the hire-purchase disbursement in respect of the above-mentioned Hirer.</p>\n        <p style=\"text-align: left;padding-bottom:10px;font-size:12px\">4. To settle you the differential sum between the capital financing redemption sum and hire-purchase loan amount; if any.</p>\n        <p style=\"text-align: left;padding-bottom:10px;font-size:12px\">5. To full settle you in the event the Vehicle Ownership Certificate of the vehicle and all necessary documents are not furnished to you within forteen (14) days as per clause (2) above.</p>\n        <p style=\"text-align: left;padding-bottom:10px;font-size:12px\">6. In the event the registration of chassis number for this vehicle is cancelled for whatever reason, you shall at your discretion re-lodged the e-Ownership into Financial Information Services under our account.</p>\n        <p style=\"text-align: left;padding-bottom:10px;font-size:12px\">7. We further agree and undertake to perform and honour all obligations and responsibilities that we have agreed to undertake and/or assume so long as such commitment are made by our officers or managers for and on our behalf or in our Company\u2019s name, and you are under no obligation and you do not owe us any duty to verify whether such officer(s) or manager(s) are duly authorized by us.</p>\n              \n     \n              <p style=\"text-align: left;font-size:12px;\">\n                    \n                    Thank you <br>\n                    \n                    Yours Sincerely,<br>\n                    <img src=\"\" width=\"80\" height=\"70\">\n                    <img src=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"50\"><br>\n                \n                -------------------------------------------- <br>\n                <b>Name <br>\n                  IC</b>\n                    \n                </p>\n              \n                 \n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"footer\">\n        <div class=\"footer-text\">\n            Rohamas Pro Autoserv Sdn Bhd (786823-T), Lot 91517, Persiaran Atmosfera Seksyen U5, 40150 Shah Alam Selangor <br>Tel: 012-8835282\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    \n        <!-- page break 2-->\n     <div class=\"page-break\"></div>\n     \n         <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"header\">\n            <p>Authorised Sales & Service Parts Dealer</p>\n            <div class=\"logo-container\">\n                <div>\n                    <img class=\"logo\" src=\"https://dcautoservices.mydotconsulting.com/files/perodua-logo.png\" alt=\"Company Logo 1\" width=\"200\">\n                    <div class=\"address\"><br>\n                        <b>ROHAMAS PRO AUTOSERV SDN BHD <span style=\"font-size:10px\">(786823-T)</span></b><br>\n                        Lot 91517 Persiaran Atmosfera Seksyen U5<br>\n                        40150 Shah Alam Selangor<br>\n                        Tel: 012-8835282\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <!--\n                <img class=\"logo\" src=\"\" alt=\"Company Logo 2\" width=\"200\" height=\"45\">\n                -->\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"letter\">\n                <br>\n                   <div class=\"section2 line\">\n                    <span class=\"section2 labels\">Date</span><span class=\"section2 colon\">:</span>\n                    <span><b>{{ frappe.utils.formatdate(doc.date, \"dd MMMM yyyy\") }}</b></span>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"section2 line\">\n                    <span class=\"section2 labels\">To</span><span class=\"section2 colon\">:</span>\n                    <span><b>AMBANK (M) BERHAD / AMBANK ISLAMIC BERHAD</b></span>\n                </div><br>\n                  \n                 <p style=\"text-align: left; text-decoration:underline\">   <strong>Confirmation of Vehicle Details for JPJ Registration via e-Hakmilik</strong><br><br></p>\n                    <p style=\"text-align: left;\">Please be informed that we have allocated a vehicle for the following customer for JPJ registration purpose:-\n<br><br></p>\n  <div class=\"section2 line3\">\n                    <span class=\"section2 labels1\">Name of Customer</span><span class=\"section2 colon3\">:</span>\n    <span><b>{{doc.customer_name}}</b></span>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"section2 line3\">\n                    <span class=\"section2 labels1\">NRIC</span><span class=\"section2 colon3\">:</span>\n                  <span><b>{{doc.nric_company_business_reg_no}}</b></span>\n                </div>\n  <div class=\"section2 line3\">\n                    <span class=\"section2 labels1\">Make & Model of Vehicle</span><span class=\"section2 colon3\">:</span>\n                    <span><b>\n                       {{doc.model}}\n                    </b></span>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"section2 line3\">\n                    <span class=\"section2 labels1\">Engine No</span><span class=\"section2 colon3\">:</span>\n                    <span><b>\n                        {% if doc.engine_no %}\n                            {{ doc.engine_no }}\n                        {% else %}\n                            &nbsp;\n                        {% endif %}\n                    </b></span>\n                </div>\n  <div class=\"section2 line3\">\n                    <span class=\"section2 labels1\">Chasis No</span><span class=\"section2 colon3\">:</span>\n                    <span><b>\n                        {% if doc.chassis %}\n                            {{ doc.chassis }}\n                        {% else %}\n                            &nbsp;\n                        {% endif %}\n                    </b></span>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"section2 line3\">\n                    <span class=\"section2 labels1\">Hp Serial No</span><span class=\"section2 colon3\">:</span>\n                    <span><b>{{doc.loan_account_number}}</b></span>\n                </div>\n  <div class=\"section2 line3\">\n                    <span class=\"section2 labels1\">Year Make </span><span class=\"section2 colon3\">:</span>\n                    <span><b>{{doc.year_make}}</b></span>\n                </div>\n              <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><br><br>\n                    \n                    Thank you <br><br>\n                    \n                    Regards,<br>\n                     <img src=\"\" width=\"80\" height=\"70\">\n                    <img src=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"50\"><br>\n                    \n                    \n                    -------------------------------------------- <br>\n                    <b>Name<br>\n                    IC</b>\n                    \n                </p>\n              \n                 \n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n                 <div class=\"footer\">\n        <div class=\"footer-text\">\n            Rohamas Pro Autoserv Sdn Bhd (786823-T), Lot 91517, Persiaran Atmosfera Seksyen U5, 40150 Shah Alam Selangor <br>Tel: 012-8835282\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>",
